            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "Draw a line between spaces that is two space edges long. All adjacent spaces must be within 10 spaces of you. Any creature must make a strength vs. intelligence roll against you in order to move or make a melee attack across the line. Any creature that attempts to move or make a melee attack across the line and fails takes 1d12 damage. At the start of each round roll a d4. If you roll a 1, the spell ends. The force field reaches 10ft into the air.",
                "marks": [],
                "data": {}
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "nodeType": "paragraph",
            "data": {},
            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "Enhance: Double the length and height of the force field",
